{"tid":1026945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬克思墓碑再遭破壞　紅油寫「種族滅絕工程師」","createTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T13:22:31.000Z","uid":54337,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f9e93c8e1e14a8893d148a1e6461374a265632","tid":1026945,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"馬克思墓碑再遭破壞 紅油寫「種族滅絕工程師」<br />\n<br />\n德國哲學家馬克思在英國倫敦的墓碑在2星期內2度遭人破壞，最近一次發生於上周五晚（15日）。有人在墓碑上以紅油寫上「仇恨教義」、「種族滅絕工程師」和「布爾什維克大屠殺紀念碑」。<br />\n<br />\n男子布洛菲爾德上周六（16日）早上跟母親到墓園時，發現馬克思的墓碑被塗鴉。他表示︰「這令人羞愧。雖然我認為紅油會被擦乾淨，但看到這麼大程度的破壞，而且發生了2次，是不好的事。」他表示不會猜測是誰做，但肯定那人十分不滿馬克思和那段歷史。該墓碑本月5日亦曾被人以鎚子破壞，管理墓園的慈善組織稱，墓碑變得不再一樣。"},{"pid":"2ae886898677ef9af94c04becb7ebb03c01def55","tid":1026945,"uid":54337,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190217/photo/bkn-20190217224741167-0217_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190218103823\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190217224741167-0217_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190218103823&h=6e3adbcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5909b1c7a2f343fa5f4206156de9793b6fa6132","tid":1026945,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190217/mobile/bkn-20190217224741167-0217_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190217%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190217224741167-0217_00912_001.html&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgNXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=f08fdf73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190217/mobile/bkn-20190217224741167-0217_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b1aab471c2417a3f5938f97b55c28ffbf32a62f0","tid":1026945,"uid":57410,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"你老母比人斬 你唔怪條友 走去怪把刀？"},{"pid":"7b2ac4997